    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a great-looking car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve kept up with the maintenance, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next big adventure! If you\u2019re looking for a reliable, well-loved vehicle that still has tons of life left in it, this is the one. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
