    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances luxury with dependable performance. The exterior features the original factory paint which maintains a high-gloss luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and entirely smoke-free; the leather upholstery remains supple and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. All electronic components\u2014including the touchscreen navigation, heated seats, and premium audio system\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, benefitting from a consistent service history. The engine idles quietly and pulls strongly, while the transmission provides smooth, predictable shifts. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service and a multi-point inspection confirming that the brakes and suspension are in solid working order. With tires that still possess deep tread, this car is ready for the road immediately without the need for any upcoming repairs.",
      "price": 33500.0,
