    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my favorite car! It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid shape\u2014honestly, it still drives like a charm. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s ready for plenty more adventures. If you\u2019re looking for a smooth ride that\u2019s been well-loved, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 31500.0,
