    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. This chassis remains structurally robust, having undergone proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure optimal lateral rigidity during high-load cornering. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that maintains excellent traction across the power band. Suspension geometry remains true, with refreshed bushings and dampers providing a communicative feedback loop through the hydraulic steering rack. While the aesthetic shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain is dialed-in for peak performance. Recent valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing service provide peace of mind for the next enthusiast.",
